name: 8-bit Adventure Map
description:
Get your ADVENTURE on with this 15" x 10" high quality inkjet print.

For all things adventure, this map has got you covered. Bones, guns, swords, monsters, and tomes -- you name it, you'll find it!

Please allow 5-7 business days for shipping.

name: Self-Indulgence - Volume 1
description:
****ONLY 5 LEFT! ORDER SOON!****

The first collected works of Gregor Holtz's autobio comic, Self-Indulgence!

Follow him from January to December (all in order, rest assured) and see what kind of boring crap he gets up to. 

Roughly 365 pages of beautifully printed comix with french flaps and a perfect binding. 

Ships media mail, so put on the kettle and wait about 7-10 bizness days.

name: Commissioned Drawing
description:
Want to commission a drawing from me? 
Well, go for it!

$6 includes shipping/handling) will get you an ink wash/watercolor drawing  of whatever the hell you want!

Want me to draw yr portrait? DONE
A picture of the Hulk puking on John Candy? Sure, why not?
How about I illustrate a diary comic for YOU? About when you finally get laid, squeeze a kid out, or bust up yr face? Cakewalk.

Just tell me what you would like me to draw in the Paypal notes, give me a handful of days to draw it, then I'll send it to you.

Easy as pie, dummy.
